WEBVTT

00:00.008 --> 00:03.967
There is somebody
in our town killing people.

00:06.768 --> 00:09.593
Local paper, came out yesterday.

00:09.728 --> 00:12.247
Evidence we found in the newspaper...

00:12.607 --> 00:14.935
Fill out your name and address
on this form.

00:15.122 --> 00:18.138
The handwriting is distinctive
enough to give us grounds

00:18.193 --> 00:19.747
to detain a suspect.

00:19.808 --> 00:20.935
He's lying about something.

00:20.966 --> 00:22.638
Did you notice him locking
the door of his study?

00:22.662 --> 00:24.083
I did.

00:24.243 --> 00:27.160
We need a record of your
whereabouts on Tuesday.

00:27.331 --> 00:29.714
I took out tours.
I can show you ticket stubs.

00:29.777 --> 00:33.222
- Leighton Thomas murdered two men.
- Twenty years ago.

00:33.507 --> 00:34.706
Dolly.

00:34.755 --> 00:36.679
He suffered a cerebral aneurysm.

00:41.219 --> 00:42.186
No!

00:42.805 --> 00:45.179
Jonjo! Oh, no, no no.

