01:33.141 --> 01:35.657
I can't believe
this is happening in my town.

01:35.990 --> 01:38.532
If you live long enough,
you see everything.

01:40.001 --> 01:41.241
Well, let's do it.

01:42.521 --> 01:45.336
Blunt instrument.
My guess... some kind of hammer.

01:45.401 --> 01:46.565
Two blows.

01:46.641 --> 01:49.846
Massive trauma to the skull.
Now, I don't know if you've seen this...

01:51.601 --> 01:54.832
When you find the hammer,
there'll be a nick in the face.

01:58.340 --> 02:00.921
- Nicole.
- Leave her alone.

02:04.641 --> 02:06.351
Serial killer.

02:07.461 --> 02:09.758
Why'd we hear that when it's too late?

02:09.913 --> 02:11.153
Why didn't you say?

02:11.241 --> 02:13.156
You should have protected him!

02:13.641 --> 02:15.185
Look at him, Frank.

02:15.521 --> 02:17.241
Look at what you've done to him.

02:19.201 --> 02:20.880
I'm sorry.

02:21.041 --> 02:23.263
Let's give them a moment, Frank, okay?

02:27.761 --> 02:29.698
I'm sorry for your loss.

